DIA_Fabio_Q602_HELLO_05_01: Well, well! Who do I see!
DIA_Fabio_Q602_HELLO_05_02: Haven't seen you in a while, Marvin, huh? How's the little brother, found?
DIA_Fabio_Q602_HELLO_Next_05_01: From the very beginning they have treated us here as someone inferior, as trash. It's time to take back from them what we deserve.
DIA_Fabio_Q602_HELLO_ShutUp_05_02: Someone's not in the mood. Why don't you hang out with us and the girls for a while. Have a little fun.
DIA_Fabio_Q602_HELLO_Dead_05_02: That bald smart-ass deserved it. Just like the whole city deserved this situation.
DIA_Fabio_Q602_HELLO_Where_05_03: She's gone, disappeared, it doesn't matter. What matters is that these beauties are here.
DIA_Fabio_Q602_HELLO_Fight_15_01: I can't let you hurt them.

DIA_Fabio_Q602_HELLO_Fight_15_03: Now you're the one who will get what you deserve.
DIA_Fabio_Q602_HELLO_Leave_15_01: You guys have fun. I have my debts to collect.
